title: Cinnamon Vegan Cakes
description: No storefront. Vegan baking service providing cakes for the weekend. Offers cinnamon-nut, halva, carrot, chocolate, and banana cakes; these are made with 50% whole wheat flour. Order by phone, text message, or email (cinnamon.vegancakes@gmail.com) by Wednesday afternoon, then pick up on Thursday or Friday afternoon.
